Package control

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddTagController
    AddTagController is the controller for adding a tag to the selected photo in the album page
    AdminPage
    AdminPage controls the administrators page after login; allows the admin to add and delete users in the app
    AlbumController
    AlbumController is the controller for the page which displays all of the photos and allows the user to do various actions upon them, such as adding a tag or captioning a photo
    AlbumViewer
    AlbumViewer is a class which allows the user to view the list of albums they currently have, and perform actions on these albums such as opening them and renaming them
    CaptionController
    CaptionController is the controller for the caption page, allowing the user to input a caption into their photo
    CopyController
    CopyController is controls copying a photo from one album into another, while keeping it in the album it is currently in
    CreateTagController
    CreateTagController controls the page for which users can create new tag types for their photos
    DeleteTagController
    DeleteTagController is a tag which controls the deletion of a tag from a photo
    DisplayController
    DisplayController manages the display of a selected photo in a view which allows them to see the date the photo was last modified, a list of tags, the caption, and the image
    GenericController
    GenericController is an abstract class which sets up the generic structure found in all controllers called by the AlbumController class
    LoginPage
    LoginPage is the controller for the login.fxml; allows for the input of a username and the login as either a user or an admin
    MoveController
    MoveController is a class which controls the movement of a photo from one album into another while deleting it from the first
    SearchAddTagController
    SearchAddTagController is a class which controls the addition of tags to the list of tags the user wishes to search their albums for
    SearchController
    SearchController is a class which controls the searching of a user's various albums in order to find a set of photos.
